  "Description": {
    "English": "An advanced nanocomputer, performing processing tasks related to starship-to-Exosuit synchronisation and security.<br><br>This part could be in working order, but will require <span class=\"name name-special\">decryption</span> before it can be installed in a new ship. A paired <span class=\"name name-stellar\">decryption terminal</span> can be located via Exosuit analysis.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一台先进的纳米电脑，可执行与飞船对套装同步和安全相关的处理任务。<br><br>该部件可能可以运作，但需要<span class=\"name name-special\">解密</span>才能安装至新的飞船。通过套装分析来定位匹配的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">解密终端</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "先進奈米電腦，能處理太空船及強化套裝同步與保全相關的任務。<br><br>此零件必須<span class=\"name name-special\">解密</span>後才能運作，並安裝到新的太空船上。可經由強化套裝分析找出對應的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">解密終端站</span>。"
  },
